Serge Gnabry: &ldquo;Personally, I think my time at Arsenal was a complete success. Playing in the Premier League allowed me to grow &amp; develop. As I&rsquo;ve said, there isn&rsquo;t a big difference between the two leagues [PL &amp; Bundesliga] &amp; I&rsquo;m pleased of my career so far.&rdquo; [Le Buteur]<br />
<br />
Gnabry on his time at Arsenal: &ldquo;At the beginning, everything went well for me. I played regularly but after that, I did less so. That being said, that experience was very enriching for me on a personal level.&rdquo;
